# Enforce LF line endings for all text in the working tree, regardless of the
# checkout platform's git core.autocrlf setting. Biome's formatter defaults to LF;
# without this, a Windows checkout (autocrlf=true) rewrites files to CRLF and
# `biome check` reports a formatting diff on every file. `* text=auto eol=lf`
# normalizes line endings on checkout so lint/format stays green everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf binary
